  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18-65 years of age

          -  Greater than or equal to 6 months post-liver transplantation

          -  Must be on a documented stable total daily dose of tacrolimus or cyclosporine for
             three months.

          -  Must have calculated creatinine clearance greater than or equal 50 mL/min
             (Cockcroft-Gault method).
      </textblock>
